Step 1: Create a scenario that triggers AppArmor denial

Modify your test application to access restricted files:

sudo nano /usr/local/bin/test-app.sh
Add:

cat /etc/passwd
Step 2: Run the application and observe the denial

/usr/local/bin/test-app.sh
Step 3: Check AppArmor logs

